<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Ectatosticta spp., dorsal view of female genitalia A E. davidi, female from Shaanxi B E. deltshevi, female from Qinghai (type locality) C E. wukong sp. nov., paratype D E. xuanzang sp. nov., holotype." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.954.52254.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/436977" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">5A, B</figureCitation>
