<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 6" captionStartId="F6" captionText="Figure 6. Ectatosticta spp., variation of female genitalia (red line, inner spermathecae (A-C, F-K) or spermathecae (D, E); green line, outer spermathecae) A-C E. deltshevi, females from Qinghai (type locality) D, E E. wukong sp. nov., paratypes F E. davidi, females from Shaanxi G-K E. xuanzang sp. nov., paratypes. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.954.52254.figure6" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/436978" pageId="0" pageNumber="17">6A-C, F</figureCitation>
